// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-0405 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 00dd93b3-1082-576a-9c99-2277494236d8

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:10*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:8*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:9*")
